title: Add support for creating docsets.
body_html:
Docsets are an offline documentation format introduced by Dash.app and supported by Zeal and some other open-source clones.

I did this for myself as I'm offline often but thought I'd see if you're interested.
If you think this is too niche to be added here, feel free to just close this PR.
